claim.claim-text:
A polarization film comprising: a polarization layer comprising;
a polymer; and
a dichroic dye having a maximum absorption wavelength in a range of 380 nanometers to 780 nanometers; and a protective layer disposed on a surface of the polarization layer and having a cross-linked structure.
